Yes, this is Today's Books.

102
00:09:09.600 --> 00:09:11.610
Yes, President Kim.

103
00:09:12.220 --> 00:09:15.780
Ah, we haven't confirmed whether the book you have ordered is in stock yet.

104
00:09:15.780 --> 00:09:18.290
Yes, I will call you as soon as that book comes in.

105
00:09:18.290 --> 00:09:20.570
Yes, goodbye.

106
00:09:20.570 --> 00:09:23.170
Hey, go and call my beeper. Something's got to be wrong with it.

107
00:09:23.170 --> 00:09:25.010
Your beeper has done nothing wrong.

108
00:09:25.010 --> 00:09:27.630
You're the one that's wrong.

109
00:09:29.180 --> 00:09:31.250
Just give up, graciously.

110
00:09:31.250 --> 00:09:34.710
Didn't you hear? Her father is the director of the prosecutor's office.

111
00:09:34.710 --> 00:09:37.400
What if he hands you a 10-year sentence?

112
00:09:37.400 --> 00:09:39.860
