How do you know?

123
00:12:19.230 --> 00:12:22.970
Your footprints in the snow.

124
00:13:06.470 --> 00:13:09.370
You're so high maintenance.

125
00:13:10.430 --> 00:13:12.830
And you're so affectionate.

126
00:13:22.950 --> 00:13:27.310
Your feet hurt don't they? Let's switch shoes.

127
00:13:31.830 --> 00:13:33.430
Ji Soo.

128
00:13:37.690 --> 00:13:40.040
I don't like war films.

129
00:13:40.920 --> 00:13:44.580
Well, of course, I hate wars more.

130
00:13:44.580 --> 00:13:47.390
Why are you bringing up war films all of a sudden?

131
00:13:49.570 --> 00:13:51.800
Whether's it's the general or an officer,

132
00:13:51.800 --> 00:13:56.030
the main protagonist always relays commands while standing in the middle.

133
00:13:56.030 --> 00:14:01.330
On the frontline, the nameless infantry take the bullets,

134
00:14:01.330 --> 00:14:03.470
and even if they are lucky enough to survive,

135
00:14:03.470 --> 00:14:07.310
the enemy general falls without a sound, from a sword or a bullet.

136
00:14:07.310 --> 00:14:13.520
But no one in there deserves to just be taken down by a gun or sword.

137
00:14:13.520 --> 00:14:18.110
Before they fell, they were all the main protagonist in their own lives.

138
00:14:19.230 --> 00:14:22.260
Even though it's just a film,

139
00:14:22.260 --> 00:14:26.990
the idea of humans being used as tools or regarded as trivial

140
00:14:28.000 --> 00:14:30.120
is something I really don't like.

141
00:14:31.930 --> 00:14:37.990
Humans should never trample on another human for any reason.

142
00:14:37.990 --> 00:14:41.400
That is another reason why I am doing demonstrations.

143
00:14:43.840 --> 00:14:46.640
And although I am not religious, I do believe there is a God.

144
00:14:46.640 --> 00:14:52.980
And that is why I believe that humans are all God's children.

145
00:14:56.940 --> 00:14:58.650
Ji Soo,

146
00:15:08.300 --> 00:15:14.880
to God, every human is a finger that hurts when it is bitten (every human is precious).

147
00:15:17.100 --> 00:15:19.770
Don't let anyone treat you poorly.

148
00:15:21.410 --> 00:15:23.620
Even if it's your family.

149
00:15:29.540 --> 00:15:35.150
Because you are a very precious

150
00:15:38.300 --> 00:15:40.480
child of God.

151
00:16:00.920 --> 00:16:03.500
You really have big feet, Sunbae.

152
00:16:05.530 --> 00:16:08.050
Is that why you have such a big heart?

153
00:16:35.750 --> 00:16:38.420
Shall I go take a look one more time?

154
00:16:38.420 --> 00:16:39.860
Let's just go.

155
00:16:39.860 --> 00:16:41.370
Yes.

156
00:16:53.750 --> 00:16:59.160
<i>You're doing things that are out of the ordinary because of that woman, right?</i>

