159
00:17:11.400 --> 00:17:15.770
About what I used to believe was right, in the past.

160
00:17:17.020 --> 00:17:20.020
It's not as if they're an organized labor movement.

161
00:17:20.020 --> 00:17:22.800
It's not as if they're using strikes as a weapon to threaten the company.

162
00:17:22.800 --> 00:17:26.300
Most of them are someone's mother or someone's grandmother.

163
00:17:26.300 --> 00:17:30.690
