164
00:17:30.690 --> 00:17:33.710
To just forcefully sweep them aside is not the answer.

165
00:17:33.710 --> 00:17:37.670
So what I wonder is, why did you become so soft?

166
00:17:37.670 --> 00:17:41.240
Why did you change so suddenly? You're scaring me.

167
00:17:41.240 --> 00:17:43.630
I may change even more, you never know.

168
00:17:43.630 --> 00:17:45.340
What does that mean?

169
00:17:45.340 --> 00:17:49.560
Because I will be making choices that are different from the ones I made before.

170
00:17:49.560 --> 00:17:51.520
