To become happy.

172
00:18:00.600 --> 00:18:03.800
So what does that mean?

173
00:18:03.800 --> 00:18:07.390
So you were not happy until now?

174
00:18:07.390 --> 00:18:09.560
I'm just talking about my beliefs.

175
00:18:09.560 --> 00:18:11.120
But isn't it the same thing?

176
00:18:11.120 --> 00:18:14.030
Why are you confusing me by using complicated words?

177
00:18:18.590 --> 00:18:22.470
Never mind anything else, but that woman,

178
00:18:22.470 --> 00:18:25.310
