195
00:19:32.520 --> 00:19:37.560
Don't worry about the taxes that come with the nominal transfer, or anything financial of the sort.

196
00:19:38.770 --> 00:19:40.410
Yes, I understand.

197
00:19:40.410 --> 00:19:45.510
But who do you think leaked this to the media?

198
00:19:47.770 --> 00:19:52.660
I believe that Director Hwang Hak Soo manages the borrowed-name accounts?

199
00:19:52.660 --> 00:19:54.490
Yes, he's done that for a long time.

200
00:19:55.400 --> 00:19:56.650
