I'm going to summon Hak Soo to investigate this matter.

203
00:20:03.290 --> 00:20:07.120
You look into the movements of the executives and the shareholders.

204
00:20:07.120 --> 00:20:09.440
Yes, I understand.

205
00:20:09.440 --> 00:20:14.370
Oh, and Seo Kyeong said she is concerned about something.

206
00:20:15.180 --> 00:20:20.090
I told you to play around a bit, but you actually played around?

207
00:20:20.090 --> 00:20:22.710
This silly girl,

208
00:20:22.710 --> 00:20:26.940
she may seem like her eyes are wandering, but you are the only one for her.

209
00:20:26.940 --> 00:20:30.100
So wrap it up, and comfort your wife.

210
00:20:33.610 --> 00:20:38.550
I cannot stand to see my child cry.

